h2.heading.heading--secondary#long-words-overflow-ellipsis Long Words: Overflow Ellipsis

p.paragraph
  :markdown-it
    The `.ellipsis` mixin asks the browser to cut long words automatically if they overflow and to add 3 dots.
    This feature is well supported, but works only for **single line**.
    See: [CanIUse text-overflow](http://caniuse.com/#feat=text-overflow)

